<i>and the destruction we see
at ancient sites on Earth.</i>

667
00:37:06.224 --> 00:37:07.934
<i>But in this case.</i>

668
00:37:08.101 --> 00:37:09.561
the extraterrestrials
were successful

669
00:37:09.686 --> 00:37:12.230
in destroying an entire planet.

670
00:37:13.356 --> 00:37:15.525
<i>Could it be
that the asteroid belt.</i>

